Global Automotive Interior Rear View Mirror Market Insights
Automotive Interior Rear View Mirror Market size was valued at USD 4.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 7.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Automotive Interior Rear View Mirror Market Overview
The automotive interior rear view mirror market was valued at approximately USD 10.85 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 14.92 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.5% during the forecast period. The rise in vehicle production, coupled with advancements in automotive technologies such as auto-dimming, electronic rearview mirrors, and integration with infotainment systems, are driving this growth. The market benefits from rising demand for enhanced safety features, increased focus on aesthetics, and the shift toward electric vehicles (EVs) that offer sophisticated interior systems.

